name: "My Boyfriend Is In Oh, Hush!" Tank Top
description:
Are you secretly dating a member of Oh, Hush!?  Is your boyfriend really a member of Oh, Hush!? Or do you just wanna tell the world "My Boyfriend Is In Oh, Hush!?"  Well now you CAN with this new tank top!! 

First 100 people to order the tank top will receive a very SPECIAL FREE SURPRISE!!! (Surprises are SOLD OUT)
